quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Kandi rwose Ibrahimu twamuhaye kuyoboka mbere (ya Musa na Haruna), ndetse twari tumuzi neza (ko abikwiye)"
  21,52,(Wibuke) ubwo yabwiraga se ndetse n’abantu be ati “Ibi ni bigirwamana ki muhora musenga?”
  21,53,Baravuga bati “Twasanze abakurambere bacu babisenga.”
  21,54,"(Ibrahimu) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri mwe n’abakurambere banyu, muri mu buyobe bugaragara.”"
  21,55,Baravuga bati “Ese utuzaniye ukuri cyangwa urikinira?”
  21,56,"(Ibrahimu) aravuga ati “Ahubwo Nyagasani wanyu (mbahamagarira kugaragira) ni Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi, ari na We wabihanze; kandi ibyo nanjye ndi umwe mu babihamya.”"
  21,57,Kandi ndahiye ku izina rya Allah! Rwose ndaza kugirira nabi ibigirwamana byanyu nyuma y’uko mugenda
  21,58,"Nuko byose arabijanjagura asiga ikinini muri byo, kugira ngo nibagaruka, (bakibaze uwagiriye nabi imana zabo)"
  21,59,(Bagarutse babona imana zabo zamenaguritse) baravuga bati “Ni nde wagize atya imana zacu? Mu by’ukuri ni umwe mu bagizi ba nabi.”
  21,60,Baravuga bati “Twumvise umusore uzivuga nabi witwa Ibrahimu.”
  21,61,Baravuga bati “Nimumuzane imbere y’abantu kugira ngo birebere (ibyo agiye gukorerwa).”
  21,62,"(Bamuzanye) baravuga bati “Ese yewe Ibrahimu, koko ni wowe wagize utya imana zacu?”"
  21,63,Aravuga ati “Ahubwo byakozwe n’iki (kigirwamana) kinini muri byo! Ngaho nimubibaze niba bishobora kuvuga!”
  21,64,"Nuko barigaya ubwabo, maze barabwirana bati “Mu by’ukuri ni mwe nkozi z’ibibi.”"
  21,65,"Nuko bubika imitwe (ariko banga kuva ku izima nyuma yo kumenya ukuri, baravuga) bati “(Wowe Ibrahimu, ni gute udusaba kuzivugisha kandi) usanzwe uzi neza ko izi (mana zacu) zitavuga!”"
  21,66,(Ibrahimu) aravuga ati “None se ni gute musenga ibitari Allah; bitagira icyo bibamarira cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bibatwara?”
  21,67,Ni igisebo kuri mwe no ku byo musenga bitari Allah. Ese nta bwenge mugira
  21,68,"Baravuga bati “Nimumutwike (Ibrahimu) maze murengere imana zanyu, niba mushobora kugira icyo mukora.”"
  21,69,Nuko twe (Allah) turavuga tuti “Yewe muriro! Ba ubukonje n’amahoro kuri Ibrahimu.”
  21,70,"Bashaka kumugirira nabi, (tuburizamo umugambi wabo mubisha) maze baba ari bo bahinduka abanyagihombo"
  21,71,Nuko tumurokorana na Lutwi (Loti) tubajyana mu gihugu (cya Shami) twashyiriyemo ibiremwa byose imigisha
  21,72,"Maze (Ibrahimu) tumuha impano (yo kubyara) Isihaqa (Isaka) tunamwongereraho Yakubu (Yakobo, umwuzukuru we). Kandi bombi twabagize intungane"
  21,73,"Twanabagize abayobozi bayobora ku bw’itegeko ryacu, tunabahishurira (ko bagomba) gukora ibyiza, guhozaho iswala no gutanga amaturo. Kandi ni twe (Allah, twenyine) basengaga"
  21,74,"Na Lutwi (Loti) twamuhaye ubushishozi mu guca imanza tunamuha ubumenyi, ndetse turamurokora tumukura mu mudugudu (wa Sodoma) wakoraga ibibi. Mu by’ukuri (abari bawutuye) bari abantu babi bakaba n’ibyigomeke"
  21,75,Twanamushyize mu mpuhwe zacu. Mu by’ukuri yari mu ntungane